Interface TagReplacer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsoupTagReplacer

    public interface TagReplacer
    Implementations of this interface aid in the modification of original HTML files by replacing tags and/or values as directed by the NodeHandler.

    Lonny

      • process

        void process(InputStream inputStream,
           NodeHandler handler,
           String baseUri,
           OutputStream outputStream)
             throws IOException
        Processes the given input stream.
        Parameters:
        inputStream - an input stream to the HTML source to process.
        handler - the handler for the nodes encountered in the source.
        baseUri - The URL where the HTML was retrieved from, to resolve relative links against.
        outputStream - the destination for the processed input stream.
        Throws:
        IOException - if an error occurs while processing the input or writing the output.
